This is a 22 minute workout called '20-Minute Bodyweight Workout for Beginners (No Repeats)' from the channel nourishmovelove.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Foundation Builder and The Comfort Moves vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.
